summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eleventh Avenue N.E. from East 52nd Street to East 45th Street in the City of Seattle, by constructing a sewer, under Ordinance No. 12934, creating Local Improvement District No. 1165 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
